{
  "name": "Recover",
  "type": "maneuver",
  "img": "icons/skills/toxins/poison-bottle-open-blood-red.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You take a moment to catch your breath and refocus.</p><p><em><strong>Range:</strong> Self</em></p><p>You attempt to spend Rest Points to regain HP equal to the Rest Points spent. Make a DC 15 Martial Check.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> You can spend 1 Rest Point.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> You can spend up to 2 Rest Points.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> You can spend 1 additional Rest Point.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> This maneuver will only calculate how many rest points you can spend – you can spend those on your character sheet.</em></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Maneuver Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Increased Healing: (1 AP or 1 SP, Repeatable)</strong> You can spend 1 additional Rest Point.</p><p><strong>Repeat Save: (1 AP or 1 SP)</strong> You can repeat a Save against an effect you’re subjected to.</p>",
